## Learned Mistakes

Add a rule every time Claude makes a mistake. One line per rule. Lead with the action.

- When curl payloads contain special characters, use `--data-raw` or a heredoc — shell expansion corrupts JSON silently
- After modifying a function signature, update all call sites in the same edit — do not leave broken mocks for a follow-up
- Run the relevant test suite before declaring a task done — "it compiles" is not a substitute for a green test run
- <Add your own learned mistakes here>

