## Agent Team Rules (add if you have more than one agent)

- Planner / Builder / Judge pattern: Judge validates within 60 seconds of Builder completion
- If a sub-agent appears stuck (no output for 30 seconds), retry with a simplified prompt
- Builder outputs a structured checklist that Judge can verify point-by-point
- Every delegation writes a handoff note to vault/handoffs/[task-id].md before dispatching

